== 主题 ==
除《其他机器人皆地狱》外，《飞出个未来》极少聚焦宗教信仰，大多数分集的剧情表明，星际快递船与公元3000年的绝大多数人类一样不信教<ref name="Gospel">{{cite book | last = Pinsky | first = Mark | title = The Gospel According to the Simpsons. Bigger and possibly even Better! edition | year = 2003 | isbn = 978-0-664-23265-8 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/gospelaccordingt0000pins/page/229 229–235] | accessdate = 2020-07-26 | url = https://archive.org/details/gospelaccordingt0000pins/page/229 }}</ref><ref name="Drawn To TV">{{cite book | last = Booker | first = M. Keith | title = Drawn to Television: Prime-Time Animation from The Flintstones to Family Guy | pages = 115–124}}</ref>。有两个宗教角色在《其他机器人皆地狱》首次亮相，分别是机器人魔鬼和莱昂内尔传教机器人牧师，之后都成为常设角色。机器人牧师说服班德加入机器人圣殿教时，语气类似典型的美国城市非裔牧师，<ref name="Gospel" />接下来发生的一系列情节都与现实生活中许多人改宗后经历类似<ref name="Gospel" />。马克·平斯基（{{lang|en|Mark Pinsky}}）指出，《其他机器人皆地狱》从两方面阐述宗教的影响：班德改宗后变得更加虔诚，虽然这在一定程度上改善他的境遇，但也导致角色身上出现不讨喜的特点<ref name="Gospel" />。班德向“罪行”屈服后机器人魔鬼出场<ref name="Gospel" />，据平斯基的著作《辛普森一家传福音》（{{lang|en|''The Gospel According to The Simpsons''}}）表述，魔鬼索取班德灵魂时的理由和许多[[美南浸信会|美南浸信会]]教义类似：“班德想要求情，但无济于事。魔鬼说‘你加入教会时就同意的’，所有美南浸信会都有这套说辞。‘你犯了罪，就该下机器人地狱——永不超生’”<ref name="Gospel" />。节目最后，班德又恢复以前的习惯，发誓永远不再做什么大善机器人或大恶机器人，这段是恶搞《[[启示录|启示录]]》中人应对信仰保持温和的说法<ref name="Gospel" />。

== 文化指涉 ==
[[File:Robot_Devil_Fiddle.png|thumb]]演奏小提琴]]

《其他机器人皆地狱》包含大量宗教戏仿情节，还有许多涉及虚构宗教主题作品的文化指涉。剧名《其他机器人皆地狱》是恶搞[[让-保罗·萨特|让-保罗·萨特]]独幕剧《[[间隔_(独幕剧)|-{zh-cn:间隔;zh-tw:密室;}-]]》（''{{lang|fr|Huis clos}}''）的著名台词“他人即地狱”<ref name="Gospel" /><ref name="Drawn To TV" />。机器人地狱各层次的惩罚和基本原理，特别是对地狱的描绘与[[但丁·阿利吉耶里|但丁]]《[[神曲|神曲]]》类似<ref name="Gospel" />。《地狱公平法》中受上帝谴责的人可以通过小提琴比赛挽救灵魂并赢得纯金小提琴，这直接取自[[查理·丹尼尔斯|查理·丹尼尔斯乐队]]（{{lang|en|The Charlie Daniels Band}}）的歌曲《[[魔鬼降临乔治亚|魔鬼降临乔治亚]]》（''{{lang|en|The Devil Went Down to Georgia}}''）<ref name="Gospel" />。编剧科恩和男演员馬吉歐都在[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]长大，所以剧中有取笑该州的笑料<ref name="keller" />。

机器人圣殿教是恶搞[[山達基教會|山達基教會]]的虚构宗教<ref name="Drawn To TV" /><ref name="gospel01">{{cite book | last = Pinsky | first = Mark | title = The Gospel According to the Simpsons | year = 2001 | publisher = Westminster John Knox Press | isbn = 0-664-22419-9 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/gospelaccordingt00mark/page/158 158–159] | url = https://archive.org/details/gospelaccordingt00mark/page/158 | accessdate = 2020-07-26}}</ref>，为此《飞出个未来》主创人格勒宁曾接到该教会电话，对两者名称相似“表示关切”<ref name="groening" />。格勒宁此前已在《[[辛普森一家|辛普森一家]]》[[辛普森一家_(第九季)|第九季]]分集《[[教派的喜悦|教派的喜悦]]》恶搞[[山達基|山達基]]<ref name="Mirkin">{{cite video | people = Mirkin, David | date = 2006 | title = The Simpsons season 9 DVD commentary for the episode "The Joy of Sect" | medium = DVD | publisher = 20th Century Fox}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last = Turner | first = Chris | title = Planet Simpson: How a Cartoon Masterpiece Defined a Generation | url = https://archive.org/details/planetsimpsonhow00turn | edition = 1st revised | year = 2005 | location = Cambridge | publisher = Da Capo Press | oclc = 670978714 | isbn = 978-0-306-81448-8 | ref = harv | page = [https://archive.org/details/planetsimpsonhow00turn/page/269 269]}}</ref>。[[美国在线|美国在线]]电视小队（''{{lang|en|TV Squad}}''）在本集评论文章之后附上提问：“机器人圣殿教是不是恶搞山达基教会？”<ref name="keller" />面对这个问题，男演员[[比利·维斯特|比利·维斯特]]（{{lang|en|Billy West}}）开玩笑叉开话题没有回答<ref name="keller" />。

== 反响 ==
《其他机器人皆地狱》是格勒宁最喜欢的四集《飞出个未来》之一，之后与另外三集一起发行{{lang|en|DVD}}套装《怪物机器人狂人乐趣收藏》（{{lang|en|''Monster Robot Maniac Fun Collection''}}）<ref name="dvdempire">{{cite web | publisher = Ravana | work = DVD Empire | accessdate = 2020-07-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150630183836/http://www.dvdempire.com/688212/futurama-monster-robot-maniac-fun-collection-movie.html | title = Futurama: Monster Robot Maniac Fun Collection | archivedate = 2015-06-30 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.dvdempire.com/688212/futurama-monster-robot-maniac-fun-collection-movie.html }}</ref>。{{lang|en|DVD}}包含格勒宁和马吉欧的评论音轨，以及《其他机器人皆地狱》的全长动画[[分镜|分镜]]<ref name="nettles">{{cite news | last = Nettles | first = John G. | title = Futurama Monster Robot Maniac Fun Collection | work = PopMatters | publisher = PopMatters Media, Inc. | archivedate = 2009-02-27 | date = 2005-08-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090227144129/https://www.popmatters.com/tv/reviews/f/futurama-monster-robot-maniac.shtml | url = http://www.popmatters.com/tv/reviews/f/futurama-monster-robot-maniac.shtml | accessdate = 2009-02-27 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。《[[温斯顿-撒冷日报|温斯顿-撒冷日报]]》（''{{lang|en|Winston-Salem Journal}}''）称赞《其他机器人皆地狱》是《飞出个未来》中表现相对优异的分集<ref>{{cite news | last = Staff | title =Adam 12 and Emergency Keep Los Angeles Safe In New DVD Sets | newspaper = Winston-Salem Journal | publisher = Factiva, from [[道琼斯公司|Dow Jones]] | date = 2005-08-27}}</ref>。[[丹·卡斯泰拉内塔|丹·卡斯泰拉内塔]]在本集和《[[魔鬼双手是非多|魔鬼双手是非多]]》（''{{lang|en|The Devil's Hands are Idle Playthings}}''）中对机器人魔鬼的诠释赢得赞誉，评论称赞他表现亮眼<ref name="Drawn To TV" />。《[[南威尔声回声报|南威尔声回声报]]》（''{{lang|en|South Wales Echo}}''）在评论《飞出个未来》第一季时特别称赞本集和《[[机器人星球的恐惧|机器人星球的恐惧]]》（''{{lang|en|Fear of a Bot Planet}}''）情节天马行空<ref>{{cite news | last = Staff | title = Win Futurama box set | work = South Wales Echo | page = 9 | publisher = Trinity Mirror | date = 2002-02-02}}</ref>。《[[世纪报|世纪报]]》的布莱恩·科蒂斯（{{lang|en|Brian Cortis}}）给予节目三星好评（最高四星）<ref>{{cite news | last = Cortis | first = Brian | title = Waging words on mediocrity — Highlights  | newspaper = [[世纪报|The Sunday Age]] | page = 5 | date = 2000-01-16}}</ref>。

《飞出个未来》在美国首播，但尚未在英国播出时，安德鲁·柯林斯（{{lang|en|Andrew Collins}}）就在《[[观察家报|观察家报]]》发文期待剧集开播，并特别称赞《其他机器人皆地狱》和《[[爱之劳工迷失太空|爱之劳工迷失太空]]》（''{{lang|en|Love's Labors Lost in Space}}''}}）<ref name="collins">{{cite news | last = Collins | first = Andrew | title = Screen: Television: Futurama looks bright: Where do you go after The Simpsons, the TV triumph of the decade? Into the 30th century, as creator Matt Groening unveils his new show, Futurama. Andrew Collins applauds. | newspaper = [[观察家报|The Observer]] | page = 2 | publisher = Guardian Media Group | date = 1999-08-22}}</ref>，认为剧中笑料充足而且信息量大<ref name="collins" />。《{{lang|en|[[PopMatters|PopMatters]]}}》杂志的约翰·内特尔斯（{{lang|en|John G. Nettles}}）认为，无论班德的角色形象，还是《飞出个未来》“玩世不恭的幽默感和狡黠的社会讽刺”，都在《其他机器人皆地狱》中体现得淋漓尽致，就连音乐曲目也“真他妈朗朗上口”<ref name="nettles" />。美国在线电视小队认为，《飞出个未来》最好笑的部分就是“机器人地狱”，特别是班德在机器人圣殿教“重生”以后<ref name="keller" />。[[DVD判决|DVD判决]]（''{{lang|en|DVD Verdict}}''）网站刊登大卫·约翰逊（{{lang|en|David Johnson}}）的评论，批评这集在班德身上花费太多笔墨<ref name="DVD Verdict">{{cite web | last = Johnson | first = David | title = Futurama: Monster Robot Maniac Fun Collection | work = DVD Verdict | publisher = David Johnson | date = 2005-08-22 | url = http://www.dvdverdict.com/reviews/futuramamrmfcoll.php | accessdate = 2016-04-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160404152838/http://www.dvdverdict.com/reviews/futuramamrmfcoll.php | archivedate = 2016-04-04 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，他对节目的整体评分为“{{lang|en|B}}”（最高为“{{lang|en|A}}”）<ref name="DVD Verdict" />。此外，[[黑马漫画|黑马漫画]]还根据节目推出漫画图书，副标题与本集相同，于2002年3月出版<ref>{{cite book | author = Dark Horse Comics | title = Futurama Pop-Out People: Hell Is Other Robots | publisher = Diamond Comic Distributors | date = 2002-03 | isbn = 1-56971-672-2}}</ref>。

